CHAT.comment: Teaching. Mother and Child sit on the floor in the living+room. Mother first teaches Child to string beads on a shoelace. Then she teaches her to sort black and white buttons into two piles. Child's speech is fairly intelligible.

u.a: tries to put bead on wrong end .
tries to put string through bead .
holds up other string with bead on it .
takes button , puts it in correct box .
puts another button in wrong box .
